com.okay.router.route

接口 IActivityRoute

  • 所有超级接口:
    IBaseRoute<IActivityRoute>, IRoute, RouteInterceptorAction<IActivityRoute>
    所有已知实现类:
    ActivityRoute, IActivityRoute.EmptyActivityRoute

    public interface IActivityRoute
extends IBaseRoute<IActivityRoute>

    Base on the IBaseRoute, This interface provided some methods to set some extras data for used by Activity.startActivityForResult(Intent, int)
